c: 11
v: 84
t: "Ke kaloku kubantu bakwa Midiyane Sathumela umzalwana wabo uShu’aybh. Wathi kubo: “Hini na bantu bakuthi! Nqulani uAllâh, aninathixo wumbi ngaphandle kwaKhe kananjalo musani ukunika (abantu) umlinganiselo onganeno kunoyimfanelo, Ndinibona nisendyebeni yaye ndiyanoyikisela kwiMini egubungelayo"